The '''Copa del Rey 1931''' is the 29th staging of the [[Copa del Rey]]. 

The competition started on April 12, 1931 and concluded on June 21, 1931 with the Final, held at the [[Estadio ChamartÃ­n]] in [[Madrid]].

==Round of 28==
* Athletic Bilbao and Sporting Gijon(because of canceling the match against the Champions of the Canary league) received a bye.

